                            <span class="pColor">정상 출금 가능해요</span>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="swiper-slide">
                        <a href="#" class="bnrBox">
                            <p class="tit">내일 결제될 예정이에요!</p>
                            <span>결제계좌(우리 10022252411712)</span>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="amountBox">
                <p class="exp">이번 달 결제 <span>3</span></p>
                <strong class="num"><i>4,210,000</i>원</strong>
